caption: We really enjoyed going to Bravo kosher pizza. We tried three different types of pizza their New York style there Square One and the white cheese one all of them were delicious. The square one had a fantastic tomato sauce layer on it which really made it taste good. The service was quick from order taking to delivery and very courteous. I highly recommend it.
